Title: downtime.py: modifying script to fix the url verification and optionally ignore ssl verification
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Component: core
Date: 1616413547
Edition: cre
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
Version: 2.0.0p2

This change modifies the url verification from checking if
it ends with /check_mk to /check_mk/. In addition, the
ignore-ssl-verification option is added which allows to bypass the ssl
verification mechanism.
